SmUtilities

Class ABCSortPairs

  • java.lang.Object
    • SmUtilities.ABCSortPairs

  • public class ABCSortPairs
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a sorting mechanism for pairs of numbers, one of which is the value to sort on and the other is an id. The pairs are added into the sorter and the id numbers are returned in their sorted order.
